    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 08/12/2024</p>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to CipherJourney. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <strong>Account Information:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Email address</li>
                <li>Username</li>
                <li>Verification token (used to verify your email)</li>
                <li>Password (stored securely with encryption)</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>User Activity:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Points earned</li>
                <li>Daily and weekly activity statistics</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Automatic Data Collection:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>IP address</li>
                <li>Browser type</li>
                <li>Operating system</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>To verify user identity during account creation</li>
        <li>To send verification emails and communicate important updates</li>
        <li>To maintain user activity statistics and enhance user experience</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations and prevent fraudulent activity</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Protect Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> All sensitive data, such as passwords, are encrypted and securely stored.</li>
        <li><strong>Access Control:</strong> Only authorized personnel can access user data.</li>
        <li><strong>Data Retention:</strong> We retain data only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes described in this policy.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties, except as required by law or to provide essential services (e.g., email delivery).</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Access to your data</li>
        <li>Request corrections to your data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Opt-out of non-essential data collection</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We may use cookies to improve your experience on our app, such as for user authentication or tracking usage trends. You can manage cookies through your browser settings.</p>

    <h2>Changes to the Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we recommend reviewing it periodically.</p>
